      <title>阿达尼驳斥美国贿赂指控，称其毫无根据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/adani-calls-us-allegations-on-250-million-bribery-as-baseless</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿达尼集团否认了美国检察官的指控，该集团亿万富翁创始人高塔姆·阿达尼及其助手涉嫌实施一项超过 2.5 亿美元的贿赂计划，以赢得印度太阳能合同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/adani-calls-us-allegations-on-250-million-bribery-as-baseless</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 07:50:30 GMT</pubDate>
